reviewText: Awesome movie

An oddball, quirkey action dark comedy.

There is  style in this set of films which is unique.  Plenty of action and violent shoot outs, plus characters which are different,  I'm glad I bought the set, cause both films are enjoyable.  Both have twist endings and good actors.  I wish they would make a SMOKIN' ACES 3. If you like quality acting, weird characters and wild shoot out scenes (like the type in QuentinTarantino's movies) you will like these films.
Original movie very good but 2nd movie lacks the complex action of the original.  Both movies are just action films with little plot.
It's a good movie collection for a great price.  Just FYI to all other buyers its a box set with two movies indivdually case not just two movies in one case.

Love love love the first movie, just insane violence, with a really decent plot.  Great ending.
2nd movie really isn't a sequel as such, more like a 2nd episode of a show called "Hitmen Shootout".  But it has enough plot twists to keep it interesting and entertaining.

I was going to just buy the first move, but for the price, it's dumb not to get the 2 pack.

Extras are pretty standard, lots of cut scenes, gag reels, interviews, etc.  Worth watching through all of them once, if you're a fan of the movie and the characters.
